Completing the NOS trinity (excluding [[NOS_Zero_Sugar]]), I have today NOS GT
Grape. The other two flavors available are [[NOS_Sonic_Sour]] and the original
[[NOS]]. Both NOS and [[Full_Throttle]] were sold to Monster in 2015. Why are
they still around? Who knows. I still love both. There were [many more
flavors](https://www.energydrinkmania.net/en/nos/) of NOS but these are the only
four I've found recently in the US. I remember seeing TURBO around 2020, but
they've discontinued it already.

