Compared to the original flavor, GT Grape is much less aggressive. Out of all
the NOS I've tried, GT Grape is the smoothest and easiest to drink. The
artificial grape taste is strong and has a light blueberry aftertaste. Its
profile is most similar to Grape Fanta, but it's carbonated and has 160mg of
caffeine.

